---
title: "Ch3.5 — Truy vấn & chẩn đoán mạng cấp thấp"
---
flowchart TD
    U["User: network info eth0"]
    CTRL["C Controller (network_mgr.c)"]
    SOCK["socket(AF_INET, SOCK_DGRAM, 0)"]
    IFR["cấu hình ifreq<br/>memset + copy 'eth0'"]
    IOCTL["ioctl(sock, SIOCGIFHWADDR, &ifr)<br/>kernel đọc driver / HW register"]
    MAC["đọc MAC từ ifr.ifr_hwaddr.sa_data"]
    CLOSE["close(sock)"]

    U --> CTRL --> SOCK --> IFR --> IOCTL --> MAC --> CLOSE
